data.description: Looking for all of the conveniences of newer construction without the headache? Completed in 2017, this beautiful home features a warm farmhouse style with an open floorplan. It's  located just off 725 in the Glencrest Subdivision. There is a huge family room and three ample sized bedrooms upstairs with a primary suite on the lower level. The primary bath has a large soaking tub, double vanity, and standalone shower. Totaling approximately 2,393 square feet. The oversized back patio was added in 2019, it's perfect for entertaining. Come see this one for yourself!
